-04-01T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前係倫敦返香港 見到cx架機真係有種回家既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係上機一刻見到D 空姐西口西面就好有家既感覺  好窩心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解我冇見過有空姐一上機就西口西面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪又同cut唔到有線一樣<br />\n人講佢又講<br />\n最後當左事實"},{"pid":"e2a156ad622859ac0a3c14a190005365cc10184d","tid":181652,"uid":24863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"同樣倫敦線，BA/CX都差唔多時間起飛，都係直航，飛行時間一樣，都係Y class，BA收九千七，CX收人萬三，CX憑咩收多人三千幾先？貪你個電視好睇啲呀？貪你CX啲service好少少咩？<br />\n有時去旅行好想俾錢搭CX，但係見到個死人價真係俾唔落<br />\nCX仲FF緊自己係premium，收緊premium價，但係你係咪俾到premium嘅服務我先？<br />\n個市場訂位又錯哂，再食老本遲早收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/232541_d71c0ad16d6f04d2ef68ec70a8e25aa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F232541_d71c0ad16d6f04d2ef68ec70a8e25aa6.jpg&h=bc4456af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/232542_488bac74551438460c0c8560104e0005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F232542_488bac74551438460c0c8560104e0005.jpg&h=ee7b0de8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de27aeafdb27934e81975ad99cdb0647f54a841c","tid":181652,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127d53d68c355b961d69d182180109c8c7572e9a","tid":181652,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CX 之前傳過國航想收購，但因為蝕緊錢，不了<br />\n收購埋就真係玩完<br />\n呢家主因仲有人搭係因為靚時間俾國泰買哂，唔係真係等執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好講到國泰得香港人坐咁, 國泰(甚至其他國家既航空公司)都係好倚賴轉機客<br />\n而轉機客個價錢都平過直航好多, 所以香港人先覺得國泰又貴又唔抵<br />\n<br />\n只要一日國泰係東南亞澳洲可以一日幾班機, 再返到香港駁到歐美機就唔會執<br />\n係香港成日話中東三寶去歐洲好抵, 對其他地方人黎講坐國泰轉機去歐美就等於我地坐中東三寶咁有讚冇彈"},{"pid":"ea6ae42c0e897a9cd4ceb93aa5be73fbc5b10d46","tid":181652,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>世界好大，香港唔只CX一間航空公司，我只係坐Y class，根本間間都差唔多，service亦唔會期望Y class俾到J class嘅質素，點解我唔揀間時間靚價錢又合理，飛行安全系數高嘅航空公司？飛機要經過檢查合格先飛得上天，呢度係香港又唔係大陸，你估航空公司可以俾錢賄賂地勤檢查人員過骨咩？CX就係睇中你地當佢係香港國航呢點，開到天價都有人搭有人打飛機，佢先會不思進取，俾埋啲垃圾過垃圾嘅service。<br />\n你地繼續俾CX搵笨柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKA嘅service就真係對得住個價<br />\n<br />\n利申：搭過CX，亦俾空姐西過面</blockquote><br />\n認同港龍good</blockquote><br />\n上次坐港龍去檳城, 個餐好好食又有哈根大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果港龍個服務唔downgrade, 我支持短途線交晒比港龍做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4b5856e9d031c78ad546b496ba6d3b2c33068a","tid":181652,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"要搵一間代表香港既航空公司我一定揀cx而唔係廚叉<br />\n<br />\n東方屌得cx好啱 呢間野真係管理不善愈做愈衰 恨鐵不成鋼 結果畀紅底加香港兩隻字就想扮晒香港出品既廚叉追住黎屌"},{"pid":"4443de1cc960bc0def16cc107c781b4c79ec47df","tid":181652,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樣倫敦線，BA/CX都差唔多時間起飛，都係直航，飛行時間一樣，都係Y class，BA收九千七，CX收人萬三，CX憑咩收多人三千幾先？貪你個電視好睇啲呀？貪你CX啲service好少少咩？<br />\n有時去旅行好想俾錢搭CX，但係見到個死人價真係俾唔落<br />\nCX仲FF緊自己係premium，收緊premium價，但係你係咪俾到premium嘅服務我先？<br />\n個市場訂位又錯哂，再食老本遲早收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/232541_d71c0ad16d6f04d2ef68ec70a8e25aa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F232541_d71c0ad16d6f04d2ef68ec70a8e25aa6.jpg&h=bc4456af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/232542_488bac74551438460c0c8560104e0005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F232542_488bac74551438460c0c8560104e0005.jpg&h=ee7b0de8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實只係差600蚊左右 屌服務差好過啦，比價真係無用<br />\n一間HK based 一間英國based<br />\n而且平飛賣晒，自然會比個貴價你，國泰Y class 都有成11~12種 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/234347_7ac23957bc72fb748b7b41416ff11312.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F234347_7ac23957bc72fb748b7b41416ff11312.jpg&h=4ba4699e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bff96d93fc02d6ce9a964e90fcad3fa786d5bf25","tid":181652,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CX 之前傳過國航想收購，但因為蝕緊錢，不了<br />\n收購埋就真係玩完<br />\n呢家主因仲有人搭係因為靚時間俾國泰買哂，唔係真係等執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好講到國泰得香港人坐咁, 國泰(甚至其他國家既航空公司)都係好倚賴轉機客<br />\n而轉機客個價錢都平過直航好多, 所以香港人先覺得國泰又貴又唔抵<br />\n<br />\n只要一日國泰係東南亞澳洲可以一日幾班機, 再返到香港駁到歐美機就唔會執<br />\n係香港成日話中東三寶去歐洲好抵, 對其他地方人黎講坐國泰轉機去歐美就等於我地坐中東三寶咁有讚冇彈</blockquote><br />\n國泰如果淨做香港客真係執撚左十世<br />\n見隔黎post 巴打屌國泰多大陸客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地full load 又屌，無客又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbd974c2797ee582193aed14f41f862cfcc789e","tid":181652,"uid":23499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>CX 之前傳過國航想收購，但因為蝕緊錢，不了<br />\n收購埋就真係玩完<br />\n呢家主因仲有人搭係因為靚時間俾國泰買哂，唔係真係等執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好講到國泰得香港人坐咁, 國泰(甚至其他國家既航空公司)都係好倚賴轉機客<br />\n而轉機客個價錢都平過直航好多, 所以香港人先覺得國泰又貴又唔抵<br />\n<br />\n只要一日國泰係東南亞澳洲可以一日幾班機, 再返到香港駁到歐美機就唔會執<br />\n係香港成日話中東三寶去歐洲好抵, 對其他地方人黎講坐國泰轉機去歐美就等於我地坐中東三寶咁有讚冇彈</blockquote><br />\n國泰如果淨做香港客真係執撚左十世<br />\n見隔黎post 巴打屌國泰多大陸客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地full load 又屌，無客又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇左咁撚多國泰post 終於都有個正常嘅comment<br />\n<br />\n全世界嘅航空公司都係玩轉機客<br />\n由其事香港靠個島仔點養得起百幾隻飛機<br />\n<br />\n再者，大部份comment 緊佢service 差嘅人都係坐緊Y class 但事實上全世界無咩airline care 你班Y 客<br />\n真係搵錢嘅係前面個四五十個位同埋係你屎忽下面堆貨"},{"pid":"65e19d72ab33c02df7f220528f6beb8c569a4311","tid":181652,"uid":24863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同樣倫敦線，BA/CX都差唔多時間起飛，都係直航，飛行時間一樣，都係Y class，BA收九千七，CX收人萬三，CX憑咩收多人三千幾先？貪你個電視好睇啲呀？貪你CX啲service好少少咩？<br />\n有時去旅行好想俾錢搭CX，但係見到個死人價真係俾唔落<br />\nCX仲FF緊自己係premium，收緊premium價，但係你係咪俾到premium嘅服務我先？<br />\n個市場訂位又錯哂，再食老本遲早收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/232541_d71c0ad16d6f04d2ef68ec70a8e25aa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F232541_d71c0ad16d6f04d2ef68ec70a8e25aa6.jpg&h=bc4456af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/232542_488bac74551438460c0c8560104e0005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F232542_488bac74551438460c0c8560104e0005.jpg&h=ee7b0de8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實只係差600蚊左右 屌服務差好過啦，比價真係無用<br />\n一間HK based 一間英國based<br />\n而且平飛賣晒，自然會比個貴價你，國泰Y class 都有成11~12種 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/234347_7ac23957bc72fb748b7b41416ff11312.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F234347_7ac23957bc72fb748b7b41416ff11312.jpg&h=4ba4699e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打，我係比較緊BA 14/9 2345起飛，CX 15/9 0025起飛嘅班次，大家起飛時間只相差40分鐘，你cap張14/9 0055嘅班次，大家差成日比較到啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aaae504c1db2e646292c0af088c94714558151a","tid":181652,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同樣倫敦線，BA/CX都差唔多時間起飛，都係直航，飛行時間一樣，都係Y class，BA收九千七，CX收人萬三，CX憑咩收多人三千幾先？貪你個電視好睇啲呀？貪你CX啲service好少少咩？<br />\n有時去旅行好想俾錢搭CX，但係見到個死人價真係俾唔落<br />\nCX仲FF緊自己係premium，收緊premium價，但係你係咪俾到premium嘅服務我先？<br />\n個市場訂位又錯哂，再食老本遲早收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/232541_d71c0ad16d6f04d2ef68ec70a8e25aa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F232541_d71c0ad16d6f04d2ef68ec70a8e25aa6.jpg&h=bc4456af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/232542_488bac74551438460c0c8560104e0005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F232542_488bac74551438460c0c8560104e0005.jpg&h=ee7b0de8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實只係差600蚊左右 屌服務差好過啦，比價真係無用<br />\n一間HK based 一間英國based<br />\n而且平飛賣晒，自然會比個貴價你，國泰Y class 都有成11~12種 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/234347_7ac23957bc72fb748b7b41416ff11312.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F234347_7ac23957bc72fb748b7b41416ff11312.jpg&h=4ba4699e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打，我係比較緊BA 14/9 2345起飛，CX 15/9 0025起飛嘅班次，大家起飛時間只相差40分鐘，你cap張14/9 0055嘅班次，大家差成日比較到啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比貴三千蚊可以知道隻眼有問題，其實係幾抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n差十分鐘都唔撚揀，係要揀差40分鐘貴d 既航班<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5TN9p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5TN9p7.jpg&h=223e5b17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48x14Je.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48x14Je.jpg&h=c3b327e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c901cae5f9226ab5c757c2e19c33247671fcbc3","tid":181652,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:08:14.000Z","msg":"對唔住 我認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次想表達CX既飛貴唔洗搞咁多野啦，直接揀個正價再同人地既promotion比就得啦"},{"pid":"fb7fc807632c74ca329322476d8c4ae02a5764c3","tid":181652,"uid":24863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"巴打，唔好意思，眼殘睇漏左呢班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96adcc770b3bc27540bca9b680aaff2b1e2b8ab8","tid":181652,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T18:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>世界好大，香港唔只CX一間航空公司，我只係坐Y class，根本間間都差唔多，service亦唔會期望Y class俾到J class嘅質素，點解我唔揀間時間靚價錢又合理，飛行安全系數高嘅航空公司？飛機要經過檢查合格先飛得上天，呢度係香港又唔係大陸，你估航空公司可以俾錢賄賂地勤檢查人員過骨咩？CX就係睇中你地當佢係香港國航呢點，開到天價都有人搭有人打飛機，佢先會不思進取，俾埋啲垃圾過垃圾嘅service。<br />\n你地繼續俾CX搵笨柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKA嘅service就真係對得住個價<br />\n<br />\n利申：搭過CX，亦俾空姐西過面</blockquote><br />\n認同港龍good</blockquote><br />\n上次坐港龍去檳城, 個餐好好食又有哈根大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果港龍個服務唔downgrade, 我支持短途線交晒比港龍做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> same 上次坐港龍去檳城都有哈根大師<br />\n好驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946543cdab23fe7bb97bb5b8dae35086190393e3","tid":181652,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd63d82fdc8685dcfa7946c28dc633b0af05393","tid":181652,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾貴d搭BA SG ANA JAL<br />\nCX? thx but no thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係貴一係平, 跟住先諗CX <br />\nHX/UO等不予考慮</blockquote><br />\n點解搭平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦自己"},{"pid":"197378f957cb124220f315a70a2f645ef39c5d59","tid":181652,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>俾貴d搭BA SG ANA JAL<br />\nCX? thx but no thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係貴一係平, 跟住先諗CX <br />\nHX/UO等不予考慮</blockquote><br />\n點解搭平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦自己</blockquote><br />\n短途幾粒鐘搭廉航咪當自己搭直通巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc078711259c937c4dc33156ffdb785e2b6b055","tid":181652,"uid":18338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前係倫敦返香港 見到cx架機真係有種回家既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係上機一刻見到D 空姐西口西面就好有家既感覺  好窩心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解我冇見過有空姐一上機就西口西面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪又同cut唔到有線一樣<br />\n人講佢又講<br />\n最後當左事實</blockquote><br />\n咪ON9 唔係之前有個𡃁仔拎把刀踩上有線總部而家會咁易CUT得到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p